Mamelodi ke lefelo leo go dulago batho ba bantshi ba mehlobo eo e fapanego le maleme a fapanego. Yona e wela ka fase ga porofense ya [[Gauteng]] yeo toropo kgolo ya gona elego [[City of Tshwane Metropolitan Municipality|City of Tshwane]], ke legae la sehlopha seo se tumilego kudu sa kgwele ya maoto elego Mamelodi Sundowns ge ba ereta "Bare sky is the limit". 

Mamelodi ke lefelo leo dinaledi tse dintshi tse di tsebegago ditswaletswe gona, go swana le bo DJ bojo mojo le ba bangwe.

